name: LEGACY: Laurel vs Yanny
description: A Quantum rift is causing people to hear different words in a viral video. Scientists have a fix but they need your help.

name: LEGACY: Home Renovations
description: You've decided to build a new house! Why not make it yourself? You'll need a lot of eggs so get started!

name: LEGACY: All or Nothing
description: A mysterious investor is looking for a lot of edible eggs. But he wants the full amount or nothing.

name: LEGACY: SpaceEggs
description: Spaceflight is booming due to re-usable rockets. Help fill the demand with this contract.

name: LEGACY: Anxiety Attack
description: A new school year and political turmoil have everyone stressed out! A regimen of medical eggs are needed.

name: LEGACY: New Civilization
description: A group of explorers are setting out to find new worlds, new civilizations. They are in need of fuel!

name: LEGACY: Tool Time!
description: It's father's day around the galaxy and power tools are flying off the shelves. Help restock!

name: LEGACY: Ouch!
description: With all those new power tools out there, there are lots of minor injuries. First Aid!

name: LEGGACY: Last Minute
description: More fireworks are needed ASAP!

name: LEGGACY: Time Tourism
description: (From Memorial Day 2018) so called "Time Tourism" is booming and Tachyon eggs are in short supply!

name: LEGGACY: Egg Day 2018
description: Some folks like to celebrate Egg Day with a bang!

name: LEGGACY: Engage!
description: (2018) The Federation of planets needs more fuel for their star fleet!

name: LEGGACY: Summer Sunset
description: The local town has commissioned you to create the waterballoons for the end of summer waterballoon fight! (2018)

name: LEGGACY: Just Chocolate
description: Sometimes chocolate demand spikes, and all we gotta do as egg farmers is make more chocolate. (2018)

name: LEGGACY: Nostalgia
description: July 14 (2018) is Egg Day around the galaxy and everyone like to celebrate with the egg that started it all...

name: LEGGACY: Getting Ready
description: With 4th of July (2018) nearing in the States, scientists have found a new way to meet the demand for fireworks...

name: LEGGACY: A Clever Solution
description: As drought wreaks havoc on agriculture, farmers are looking for water in unusual places... (2018)

name: LEGGACY: Mother's Day Brunch
description: Mothers all over the galaxy are requesting omelettes and french toast for breakfast! (2018)

name: LEGGACY: Complex Costumes
description: Halloween (2018) costume manufacturing has started. These are sophisticated scary costumes that need some high tech components.

name: LEGGACY: Chocolate!
description: Didn't take scientists long to figure out the smart thing to do was to just make chickens lay chocolate eggs. (2018)

name: LEGGACY: Fall Festival Competition
description: The (2018) Fall Festival egg laying competition is here!

name: LEGGACY: Super Food Drive
description: (2018) Egg Farmers have flocked to high value eggs leaving people hungry! We need some Superfood eggs stat!

name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Crunch
description: (2018) Pumpkins are in super high demand... leave it to the chickens to deliver the goods!

name: LEGGACY: A New Sun
description: (2018) A new solar system has been found with multiple habitable planets in need of terraforming!

name: LEGGACY: Moon Food
description: (2019) Moon colony food stores were tainted without government food inspectors to check for contaminants. Help send some food!

name: LEGGACY: Halloween Blitz
description: (2018) Pumpkin demand is overwhelming! A quick contract for big money!

name: LEGGACY: Fusion Tankers
description: The world's largest ocean shipping company is putting ultra compact fusion reactors in all their tankers. Long term work available.(2018)

name: LEGGACY: Moon Rockets
description: Moon colony food stores were tainted. The food is ready on earth, just need more fuel! (2019)

name: LEGGACY: Wildfires
description: (2018) Climate change is wreaking havoc on dryer climates. Wildfires are rampant but now there is a way egg farmers can help! (Egg, Inc. has donated $500 to the American Red Cross)

name: LEGGACY: World Record Egg
description: (2019) With a simple picture of an Egg becoming the most liked social media post, demand for the classic is booming!

name: LEGGACY: The Thaw
description: (2019) Half the USA is frozen over from an Arctic Blast! Fusion egg reserves are depleted for home heaters and de-icers.

name: LEGGACY: Resolutions
description: It's that time of year, everyone is headed to the gym and getting on a strict diet of Superfood Eggs!

name: LEGGACY: Quantum Trash Bags
description: (2018) With all the wrapping paper and boxes to throw out, Quantum Trash bags are flying off the shelves!

name: LEGGACY: History Lesson
description: (2019) In appreciation of Martin Luther King day people around the world take a trip back to witness first hand key moments in world history!

name: LEGGACY: Galactic Outreach
description: (2019) An emerging civilization needs to fight a health epidemic but is not ready for more advanced eggs. We need your help!

name: LEGGACY: Space Vacation
description: (2019) Space Tourism is way up this year and there are rocket fuel shortages everywhere!

name: LEGGACY: Love is in the Air
description: (2019) Valentine's day is here and boxes of chocolates are flying of the shelf!

name: LEGGACY: Teslegg Model F
description: (2019) After a long wait Teslegg has released their mass market fusion powered car! Fusion eggs are in high demand.

name: LEGGACY: Back to the Moon
description: (2019) With renewed plans to colonize the moon, rocket fuel is in high demand. Let us boldly go!

name: LEGGACY: Fusion Exclusion
description: (2019) Smaller settlements all over the galaxy still use Fusion Egg Reactors and are running short of Fusion Eggs!

name: LEGGACY: Spring Cleaning
description: (2019) Spring Cleaning is starting early due to the wild popularity of Marie Kondo's new book. Quantum storage is in high demand!

name: LEGGACY: Hangover Cure
description: It's the day after St. Patrick's day and folks had a little too much to drink, hangover cures are out of stock!

description: A science project aims to move a planet into the habitable zone of a nearby star system. Graviton egg demand is spiking.

name: LEGGACY: Diapers Everywhere!
description: (2019) The creator of Egg, Inc. (me) just had a baby!  I need y'all to work together to make me some quantum waste pails to help with all the diapers!

name: LEGGACY: Spring is Here
description: (2019) What a beautiful day isn't it? No better way to start off the day than with 2 fried eggs, at it appears everyone agrees.

name: LEGGACY: April Fool
description: (2019) A tech company's April Fools jokes went too far causing trillions in damages. Let's go back in time and stop the bad jokes!

name: LEGGACY: CleanX
description: (2019) To make room for more satellites, we need to clean up space! Over 500,000 pieces of space trash need to be pulled back to earth. So we're building a Graviton Canon!

name: LEGGACY: Easter Egg Shortage
description: (2019) With so many planned easter eggs hunts around the galaxy, there is a shortage. We need your help!

name: LEGGACY: The New Mac Pro!
description: (2019) Apple has placed an huge order of Super Material eggs for the crazy new Mac Pro case!

name: LEGGACY: Housing Boom!
description: (2019) There are housing shortages all over the galaxy, the building boom needs more Super Material eggs to catch up!

name: LEGGACY: Mother's Day Begins
description: (2019) Chocolate makers are trying to get a jump on Mother's day this year. Help them out with this endurance contract.

name: LEGGACY: Cinco de Oh-no

name: LEGGACY: Heat Waves
description: (2019) Heat waves are being reported all over the planet, help everyone cool off!

name: LEGGACY: Edible Shortage
description: (2019) With the discovery of new Boosts, farmers are quickly moving to pricier eggs leading to a scarcity of Edible Eggs, we need your help!

name: LEGGACY: School's Out!
description: (2018) A new batch of students have earned their certification to consume Prodigy Eggs!

name: LEGGACY: Tachy-gone
description: (2020) "Time tourism" broke all records this memorial day depleting tachyon egg inventories, time to help stock back up!

name: LEGGACY: 3D Printing
description: (2019) 3D printing is blowing up and there are filament shortages all over, Super Material eggs are needed!

name: LEGGACY: Ten for Ten
description: (2019) It's a busy time of year for bakers, orders for Edible eggs have quadrupled!

name: LEGGACY: Superfood Mystery
description: (2019) A mysterious company is buying incredible amounts of Superfood Eggs, can you meet the demands?

name: LEGGACY: Waterballoon Fight!
description: (2019) The longest day of the year is here (norther hemisphere) and you know what that means!

name: LEGGACY: New Formula
description: (2020) The genetic formula has been tweaked this year leading to record demand for firework eggs this year!

name: LEGGACY: Summer Activities
description: (2019) Summer activities are at an all time high, and that means so are injuries! Help meet the demand for Medical eggs.

name: LEGGACY: Summer Heat
description: (2019) With summer heat in full swing, AC is running non stop and some power plants need more fuel!

name: LEGGACY: Moon Vacation
description: (2019) Folks are squeezing in their final summer trips and the Moon is this years most popular destination, more fuel is needed!

description: (2019) While advanced eggs have made energy clean, Rooftop solar panels are still saving people money! Help meet demand for raw materials!

name: LEGGACY: Folding Screens
description: (2020) While it is unclear who wants a folding screen, at this year's Consumer Electronics Show they were all the rage! Raw materials are needed!

name: LEGGACY: CyberSteel
description: (2019) Despite controversial styling the new Truck from Teslegg has become a must have for Egg Farmers. More raw materials are needed!

name: LEGGACY: Something Out There
description: (2020) The discovery of the remains of an ancient civilization in a distant solar system has caused a resurgence of deep space exploration!

name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Prep
description: (2019) Halloween looking to be big this year, Pumpkins are sold out and more are needed

name: LEGGACY: Air Conditioning
description: (2019) With heat waves sweeping the southwest, Air Conditioners are running non stop, more fuel is needed for Fusion reactors!

name: LEGGACY: Leap Year Festival
description: (2019) Leap Year Festivals around the world need Tachyon eggs for various rituals!

name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Time!
description: (2019) It is officially Fall (in the northern hemisphere), you know what that means! Pumpkin all the things!

name: LEGGACY: Tummy Aches
description: (2019) Kids are eating too much candy after Halloween and it's causing shortages of stomach medication!

name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Pie

name: LEGGACY: More Pumpkins?!

name: LEGGACY: Leftovers
description: (2018) Thanksgiving has left the world with too many leftovers, quantum Tupperware is sold out everywhere, and more raw materials are needed.

name: LEGGACY: Stuffed
description: (2019) Folks have been over-eating for days and are looking for lighter meals, Superfood eggs are flying off the shelves

name: LEGGACY: Outbreak
description: (2020) The word races to contain and support the outbreak of a new virus. Get the facts from your local government health agency (eg. cdc.gov)

name: LEGGACY: Shop at Home
description: (2020) With the incredible surge of at home delivery for just about everything Quantum storage solutions are booming!

name: LEGGACY: Winter Break
description: (2018) It's Winter Break! And since break homework was deemed cruel and unusual punishment, Prodigy Eggs are all the rage!

name: LEGGACY: Last Minute Shipping
description: (2019) Shipping companies are slammed! More Quantum storage is needed!

name: LEGGACY: Hangover Cure
description: (2019) The big new years parties are scheduled, partiers are planning ahead this year and buying hangover cures before hand!

name: LEGGACY: I Have a Dream
description: (2019) As recent the battle for civil rights may be, we none the less must look back to understand our present.

name: LEGGACY: Restoration
description: (2020) Recently returned interplanetary artifacts posses mysterious properties, archeologists are trying to restore them to see what power they might possess

name: LEGGACY: Arts and Crafts

name: LEGGACY: Chocolate Rush

name: LEGGACY: Quantum Blitz

name: LEGGACY: Secret Projects

name: LEGGACY: Video Games
description: (2020) With folks playing more PC and Console games than ever before, home energy needs are up!

name: LEGGACY: Ion Drive

name: LEGGACY: Egg Pre Orders
description: (2020) Easter is around the corner, so naturally store are starting to stock up!

name: LEGGACY: Chocolate Refill
description: (2020) The shelves of chocolate are empty at grocery stores, help fill the new orders!

name: LEGGACY: Cool Off
description: (2020) As heat waves take over the country, waterballoons are in short supply!

name: LEGGACY: Snack Attack
description: (2020) For an unknown reason baked goods are flying off the shelves and more eggs are needed to restock!

description: (2019) It's time to file taxes! Headache cures are in high demand. Help fill the orders!

description: (2020) Bluetooth enabled pigs are the new hot pet! Neuro-implant makers need more materials!
